{"tid":1428376,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【支持警方執法】懷疑李桂華涉嫌妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:11:17.000Z","uid":290285,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48a9274af9bc4d5aeeeb27633a21636982862524","tid":1428376,"uid":290285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華，於記者會上有預謀地使用不科學實驗展示觀星筆，並多次使用坊間重未聽聞的名字「鐳射槍」稱呼證物。<br />\n<br />\n在場記者質疑是否有誤導公眾及日後陪審團之疑，李桂華並未正面回答，亦指自己未曾質詢律政師意見，自己認為並無不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n▶妨礙司法公正（Perverting the course of justice）出自英格蘭和愛爾蘭法律，是指犯罪者在司法過程中通過干擾、欺騙等手段，使法庭作出偏向自己或第三者的判決，以致公義無法獲得彰顯。妨礙司法公正是普通法地區的一種刑事罪，為可公訴罪行之一。由於普通法中沒有就可公訴罪行定下特別的罰則，所以可判處的監禁刑期並沒有上限[1]。理論上最高刑罰是終身監禁，但現代已經少有罰得如此重的案例。<br />\n<br />\nsource: wiki <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=ccb61215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持警方對李桂華展開調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7a9e5d8acaeb28f7f6d4f22cdb1c40319d6b5b1a","tid":1428376,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"查佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d3a64fb3d0eba7857d9ceea31f34cdfb45bce3","tid":1428376,"uid":290285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"20e240ccd3c6e272b208c078726d27b90bb0b64e","tid":1428376,"uid":290285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"72d0186ca01f7320f5e48654eb45eb6255134560","